  </div>
</div>

<hr class="featurette-divider">

<div class="row featurette">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Let FARManager help your field performance. <span class="text-muted">Improved yields.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Export your field data to an excel document. Observe charts and graphs about your field performance. Use these analytics to make smarter decisions. </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <%= link_to image_tag("fieldstats.png", class:"img-responsive featurette-image", alt: "Field Statistics")  %>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="featurette-divider">

<div class="row featurette">
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <%= link_to image_tag("cropcheck.png", class:"img-responsive featurette-image", alt: "Crop Check")  %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Record all crop checks permanently. <span class="text-muted">Never forget again!</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Hail. Disease. Pests. Frost. Wind. These all are a farmers worst enemy so make the crop check battle a little easier. FARManager allows you to easily record these to reference for years to come. </p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="featurette-divider">

